Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.77,2:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.34,2:11:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, on the way to this venue,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.12,2:12:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked the sloped road 'Sakura-zaka'  (Proof Readers note: Cherry blossom hill?) which leads to the entrance of Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.31,2:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry trees were in full bloom and it was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.67,2:12:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt we can have this ceremony at a very opportune time.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.08,2:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing cherry blossoms used to make me think,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:15.80,2:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now spring has come...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.63,2:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting warm...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:19.39,2:12:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon we'll have a cherry-blossom viewing...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.74,2:12:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But in these past few years,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:25.95,2:12:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the cherry blossom makes me think of the graduation of Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.22,2:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and that makes me very emotional.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.72,2:12:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,While seeing the cherry blossom,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.02,2:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I recollected my first impression of you four graduates.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:47.24,2:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuno was so short,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.49,2:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and was always spinning around and chanting something strange.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.17,2:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought 'Is she OK?'
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.11,2:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kikuchi also was short
Dialogue: 0,2:13:06.01,2:13:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but she was emitting an atmosphere like she can see right through everything...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.07,2:13:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt she could read me like a book,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.57,2:13:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, 'Is it possible, THIS small girl being like that?'
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.16,2:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,'What the hell is she going to be?'
Dialogue: 0,2:13:19.07,2:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When I met Taguchi for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:21.76,2:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,she was like a doll and was absent-minded
Dialogue: 0,2:13:25.53,2:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought, 'Err...there is still no soul installed into this doll...'
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.16,2:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,'Is she all right?'
Dialogue: 0,2:13:34.44,2:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And Notsu...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:36.85,2:13:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe because she was already a middle schooler,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.81,2:13:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt she was over-familiar with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.29,2:13:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She was like an old hand with a lot of experience
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.12,2:13:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.32,2:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A while later, I heard Notsu had been very nervous,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:57.41,2:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,she was doing her best to find out what her charm is, and what lies in herself.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.26,2:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I named her as the Talk-Chairperson.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:08.21,2:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she has had a tough year.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:12.84,2:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I heard you saying on the stage
Dialogue: 0,2:14:16.51,2:14:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,'At first, Koubaibu was terrible'
Dialogue: 0,2:14:18.84,2:14:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was, and I felt very uneasy,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:20.72,2:14:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but you made a great improvement.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.56,2:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, your MCing was really adorable.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.11,2:14:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And, as of Taguchi,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.04,2:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a soulless doll gradually gain a wonderful soul
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.56,2:14:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and, as the Spirit Chairperson, she really stirred up everyone's spirits,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.89,2:14:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and your performance was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.56,2:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching Sakura Gakuin from the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.79,2:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and two of the founding members Mizuno and Kikuchi
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.60,2:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,are graduating after a long five years,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.38,2:15:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes me very emotional.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.27,2:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know these two girls
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.00,2:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,have come through everything in Sakura Gakuin since they were 5th graders.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.04,2:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.56,2:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They have overcome a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:15.74,2:15:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And furthermore, a club activity they've been performing with
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.80,2:15:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,achieved unbelievable success and they've made the world their stage.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.84,2:15:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But even in such a sensation
Dialogue: 0,2:15:31.74,2:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of them never put Sakura Gakuin activities aside.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.97,2:15:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply impressed.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:38.91,2:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've kept watching you, and found the meaning, the significance of Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:49.72,2:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In your growth period --
Dialogue: 0,2:15:51.68,2:15:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when you make great improvement physically and mentally,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.44,2:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you are burdened with heavy tasks,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.94,2:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and you must overcome one task after another.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.39,2:16:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've got tons of problems and troubles
Dialogue: 0,2:16:06.48,2:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but you yourself have decided to be here because you love performing,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.91,2:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so all of you have never been discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.81,2:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the essence of Sakura Gakuin, I think,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.36,2:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and that nature enables you to improve a lot, in a short period.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:30.18,2:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we, human beings use only 10% of
Dialogue: 0,2:16:35.76,2:16:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the potential ability of our brain.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:41.36,2:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,90% of the ability is inactive.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.10,2:16:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in a specific situation,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.53,2:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,through extraordinary effort,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:51.68,2:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we can activate the latent power of our brain.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:57.64,2:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you have activated, unlike ordinary people,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:03.36,2:17:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,20% or 25% of your brain.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.99,2:17:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you can't achieve these amazing performances.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:10.42,2:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Fukei-san?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:18.31,2:17:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To dance such an elaborate choreography while singing,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.84,2:17:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and to have a talk just after dancing...
Dialogue: 0,2:17:28.88,2:17:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:31.63,2:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be proud of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:33.40,2:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:37.37,2:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've already grown to become 'Super'.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:42.33,2:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe 'the days of women' are coming to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:46.68,2:17:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A bright future, a peaceful world will arrive being lead by women.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:55.38,2:18:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, there will be many female opinion leaders,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:00.07,2:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and they will take initiative in making this world better.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.68,2:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you study the career
Dialogue: 0,2:18:09.48,2:18:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of female opinion leaders you'll find
Dialogue: 0,2:18:13.54,2:18:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,'What?'
Dialogue: 0,2:18:14.79,2:18:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,'Is she a graduate of Sakura Gakuin?'
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.33,2:18:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,'And this one also is!?'
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.88,2:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my dream, and I think it'll really happen.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:25.82,2:18:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to the future.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:27.97,2:18:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So please don't be hesitant to make a big impact on the world after your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:32.44,2:18:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about what people say,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:34.89,2:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because everyone here knows what you've done in Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.68,2:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone can't help being on your side,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:42.66,2:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot help but support you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:46.22,2:18:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.87,2:18:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep supporting them after their graduation.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:57.51,2:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And remaining members...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:06.01,2:19:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep trying your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.51,2:19:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, there will remain really few students.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.82,2:19:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.62,2:19:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very worried about what will come.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.09,2:19:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So the four of you,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:20.62,2:19:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,please come and give them good advice.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:22.83,2:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:24.01,2:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your attention, this is all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.19,2:19:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Principal Kuramoto Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:29.05,2:19:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
